<BaseLayout title="About The Career Insights" description="Learn how The Career Insights supports organizations, professionals, small businesses, cleared talent, and military veterans.">
  <section class="page-hero about-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow light">About</p><h1>We make the path from workforce need to proven capability clearer.</h1><p>Practical talent systems for public, private, and commercial organizations across the United States and globally.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section dotted-section"><div class="shell split-intro"><div><p class="eyebrow">Who we are</p><h2>The Career Insights.</h2></div><div class="rich-copy"><p class="lead">Our methodology starts with the critical requirement, not a generic pool of resumes.</p><p>We use targeted database filtering and a stringent verification process to present qualified candidates who are fully vetted for relevant certifications and clearances. The result is a faster, more confident path to placement.</p><p>We also empower professionals at every stage of their career journey through personalized guidance, expert insight, skill development, and ongoing support.</p><a class="text-link" href="/contact">Need staffing assistance? <span>↗</span></a></div></div></section>
  <section class="section section-gray"><div class="shell section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">Overview</p><h2>Affordable talent access with specialist reach.</h2></div><p>TCI supports temporary and direct hire across public, private, and commercial sectors, with a focus on helping small businesses grow through practical hiring solutions.</p></div><div class="shell about-stats"><article><strong>Public</strong><p>Government, contractors, cleared roles, and public programs.</p></article><article><strong>Private</strong><p>Technology, finance, healthcare, operations, and professional functions.</p></article><article><strong>Commercial</strong><p>Direct hire, contingent recruiting, staffing, and project delivery.</p></article></div></section>
  <section class="section veteran-section"><div class="shell split-intro"><div><p class="eyebrow">Military veterans</p><h2>Supporting the transition back into the workforce.</h2></div><div class="rich-copy"><p class="lead">We are committed to helping military veterans find meaningful employment while helping employers meet veteran hiring goals.</p><p>Our staffing areas include information technology, cybersecurity, healthcare, finance, executive search, and program and project management. TCI is committed to equal opportunity employment for qualified people regardless of sex, race, religion, ethnic origin, or any other legally protected status.</p></div></div></section>
  <section class="section section-gray company-paths"><div class="shell three-grid"><article id="careers"><span>01</span><h3>Careers</h3><p>Join a team focused on practical impact, trusted delivery, and better workforce outcomes.</p><a href="/contact">Explore careers ↗</a></article><article id="partners"><span>02</span><h3>Partners</h3><p>Extend delivery through aligned technology, training, recruiting, and implementation partnerships.</p><a href="/contact">Become a partner ↗</a></article><article id="clients"><span>03</span><h3>Clients</h3><p>Work with a responsive team built around your goals, constraints, and operating environment.</p><a href="/contact">Talk to our team ↗</a></article></div></section>
